    <p>This is not the easiest of trips.  I came from Chaing Mai so this involved another 9 hour overnight train ride to Bangkok.
        An 8 hour layover in Bangkok.  Another 8 hour overnight trainride to Surat Thani followed by a Bus ride and a Katamaran.
        All worth it!!! The most beautiful place ever!!!!
    </p>
    <h5>Muay Thai</h5>
    <p>One of the best parts of Thailand is the muay thai training. I found a place down the road called Diamond Muay Thai
        and got a few private lessons.  As always, everything is super cheap so there are no down sides.  
    </p>
